                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "44": {
                                          "id": "44",
                                          "speaker": "Saer Grotpoll",
                                          "text": "We just want Baldur's Gate to be for Baldurians. Let Waterdeep give this riffraff shelter.",
